  <h3>Chapter 4: Flexible Navigation</h3>

  @Status(HomeController.ChapterStatus.InEditing)

  <p>Flexible navigation is a special case of flexible layouts but is an important one. We go through
    a number of ways of solving layout problems in responsive scenarios.
  </p>

