  <h3>Chapter 6: Displays Modes, View Engines and HTML Helpers</h3>

  @Status(HomeController.ChapterStatus.InEditing)

  <p>In this chapter we dive into ASP.NET MVC, discussing its ways of rendering markup and
    how we can leverage those to provide the flexibility we need for mobile.
  </p>

  <h3>Chapter 7: Device and Feature Detection</h3>

  @Status(HomeController.ChapterStatus.InEditing)

  <p>Sometimes it is crucial to know something about the device visiting the page or its capabilities.
    Here we discuss strategies for doing this.
  </p>

